{"tid":2424712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"洗手梘液洗完手滑潺潺乾唔乾淨??","createTime":"2021-02-26T20:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T20:49:38.000Z","uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"654a662208292ade285cdd977de9b9902647363b","tid":2424712,"uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:02:05.000Z","msg":"之前用番梘洗得手多，對手皮膚好乾。<br />\n後來買咗洗手梘液，希望潤少少，冇咁乾燥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係諗諗吓，洗手都係要洗走啲武肺病毒，但家陣洗完反而有嘢包住啲皮膚。<br />\n會唔會洗唔走啲武肺病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a59562f0f1432e31c4ea3e42b1d2f5a9c75266","tid":2424712,"uid":392943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:04:21.000Z","msg":"用滾水好似會冇咁冼"},{"pid":"bbff80e15bed73b855421f9c2630f867bfa314dc","tid":2424712,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:06:04.000Z","msg":"會呀，用火酒再點著佢最穩陣"},{"pid":"be60f64c14e797de67dec8e0e53c8da20cd8666b","tid":2424712,"uid":166885,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:08:09.000Z","msg":"聽講要強酸（鏹水） 或強鹼（漂白水） <br />\n內服外用，357個時辰一次。<br />\n連啫啫一齊用。"},{"pid":"d29ca780f36deed4c0b61abb01876036ab9c8ae4","tid":2424712,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:23:06.000Z","msg":"用酒精搓手液咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水都慳返呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f76c042da0c7c8276eaf0b7c14aef606358f8d","tid":2424712,"uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbff80e15bed73b855421f9c2630f867bfa314dc","tid":2424712,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:06:04.000Z","msg":"會呀，用火酒再點著佢最穩陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:33:17.000Z","msg":"又啱"},{"pid":"6cf447dd4477322b04ad0b0d91066827aa19d49a","tid":2424712,"uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d29ca780f36deed4c0b61abb01876036ab9c8ae4","tid":2424712,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:23:06.000Z","msg":"用酒精搓手液咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水都慳返呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:33:52.000Z","msg":"好似話酒精有啲菌或者病毒殺唔死"},{"pid":"e8a9d7005d890915956edbd292082e8d5a34abe6","tid":2424712,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:49:38.000Z","msg":"我會搽番梘洗甩啲梘液"}]}